title: Black-Eyed Susan Acoustic Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Beer/Wine, Delivery, Take-out, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Serves freshly made-in-house from scratch food in a casual atmosphere. Vegan dishes (also gluten free) are clearly marked and are available breakfast, lunch and dinner. Always has made-in-house vegan sorbet or fresh fruit.  Live acoustic music on Fridays and Saturdays.Uses locally-sourced.
